        "release_date": "1980-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "Embark on an innovative journey through the ECOEDILE VIRTUAL EXHIBITION, a visionary project conceived by Enzo Nembrini, the artistic director of Ecoedile Srl, and passionately animated by Rischa Paterlini, marking the advent of a revolutionary era in artistic curation.\n\nInspired by the breathtaking beauty of a legendary quarry on the enchanting island of Menorca, this exhibition presents a private collection within an extraordinary outdoor landscape. Visitors are invited to contemplate the symbiotic relationship between architecture, art and nature, going beyond the conventional boundaries of the gallery. The unique aerial perspective, similar to that of a drone, gives visitors a panoramic view of the exhibition, arousing an exciting sense of discovery and wonder.\n\nThis digital museum amplifies accessibility and inclusivity, aspiring to foster a deeper connection with the art, architecture and rich cultural heritage of Bergamo.\n\nEmbrace the limitless potential of the ECOEDILE VIRTUAL EXHIBITION, redefining the boundaries of artistic exploration and community interaction, paving the way for a new era of cultural exchange and creative expression.",
